      "para_id": "Q001097.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , Enlil’s warrior , En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , built a coach-house ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001097.8",
      "line_range": "8",
      "translation": "(8) The personal god of En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of the coach-house , is Šul-MUŠxPA ."
    }
  ],
